ision, the area blocks line of sight and is totally obscured. Creatures without darkvision are blinded while in the area. Light sources do not function in the darkness.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Triggered</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Blood Frenzy&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Trigger:&lt;/i&gt; The lightdrinker is first bloodied.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect (Immediate Reaction):&lt;/i&gt; The lightdrinker uses night’s maw twice.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Blood Frenzy</b> ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> The lightdrinker is first bloodied.</p><p><i>Effect (Immediate Reaction):</i> The lightdrinker uses night’s maw twice.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Light Burst&lt;/b&gt; (radiant) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Trigger:&lt;/i&gt; The lightdrinker drops to 0 hit points.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack (No Action):&lt;/i&gt; Close burst 1 (creatures in the burst); +15 vs. Reflex&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 2d6 + 9 radiant damage, and the target is blinded until the end of its next turn.&lt;/p&gt;]] ᗕ <b>Light Burst</b> (radiant) ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> The lightdrinker drops to 0 hit points.</p><p><i>Attack (No Action):</i> Close burst 1 (creatures in the burst); [[/roll 1d20+15[ vs. Reflex]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Light Burst&lt;/b&gt; (radiant) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack (No Action):&lt;/i&gt; Close burst 1 (creatures in the burst); &lt;u&gt;+15 vs. Reflex&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 2d6 + 9#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Light Burst&lt;/b&gt; (radiant) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;